WEBVTT

00:02:56.060 --> 00:03:00.559
to see women’s cricket reach such a level

00:03:00.559 --> 00:03:06.909
that the whole world is watching at such 
a big occasion, such a big platform ...

00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:11.480
if I could be nervous, then for them, 
who were there for the very first time,

00:03:11.490 --> 00:03:13.800
That's why as a captain

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:17.690
I am proud of the way that the team 
has performed throughout the tournament

00:03:17.690 --> 00:03:21.729
I told them that even though we lost,

00:03:21.729 --> 00:03:25.628
I’m thankful that I could experience
playing the World Cup finals.

00:03:25.628 --> 00:03:29.350
If we had lost before the semi-finals
or lost the semi-finals,

00:03:29.350 --> 00:03:34.210
then I wouldn’t have been able 
to experience this atmosphere.